{
  "texts": [
    "This enhancement is vividly depicted in the chart presented in Figure 2, which compares the performance of the original Mistral model and the PIL-enhanced version across four specific tests from the Google BIG-Bench test set: Analogical Similarity, Analytic Entailment, Arithmetic, and Boolean Expressions.",
    "Fig. 2: Accuracy Improvement in Retrieving Factual InformationIn the \"Analogical Similarity\" test, which measures the model's proficiency in identifying relationships between different events, the PIL-enhanced Mistral showed a significant performance leap.",
    "This improvement suggests a deeper understanding of underlying patterns and analogies in varied contexts, an essential aspect of sophisticated language comprehension.",
    "The \"Analytic Entailment\" test, which focuses on the model's ability to determine logical entailment between sentences, also saw a notable enhancement.",
    "Here, the PIL's impact is clear in its contribution to the model's logical reasoning capabilities, allowing for more accurate parsing and understanding of complex sentence structures and their logical connections."
  ]
}